data.meta_description: Arthur Wellesley, 1st Duke of Wellington was born on May  1, 1769 in Mornington House, 24 Upper Merrion Street, Dublin, Co Dublin, Ireland, son of Garret Colley Wellesley 1st earl of Mornington and Anne Wesley (born Hill-Trevor) Countess of Mornington Hill-Trevor. He died on September 14, 1852 in Walmer Castle, Walmer, Kent, England. This information is part of M(a)cDonald Family Site - black Jewish YAHYA family line 3 by Dr Wilton McDonald- black Hebrew on Genealogy Online.
